War Master's Charge					KEY:Warblade Martial Discipline ~ War Master's Charge					SORTKEY:Maneuvers and Stances	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Warblade Martial Maneuver.White Raven.White Raven Discipline.White Raven Maneuver.Maneuver.Martial Maneuver.Strike					PREABILITY:4,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.White Raven Maneuver					PREVARGTEQ:InitiatorManueverLVL,9		DESC:With a great battle cry, you lead your allies in a devastating charge. Fired by your commanding presence and deftly led by your supreme grasp of tactics, you and your allies form an unstoppable wedge. You are an inspiring figure on the battlefield, allowing you to lead others on attacks that would strike fear and doubt into even the stoutest warrior's heart. Under your leadership, the group becomes much more than the sum of its parts. As part of this maneuver, you charge an opponent. In addition, all allies within 30 feet of you at the beginning of your turn can also charge this target as an immediate action. You and allied creatures do not block each other when determining if you can charge. Your charge attack deals an extra 50 points of damage, and those of your allies each deal an extra 25 points of damage. For each ally who charges, counting yourself, your charge attack and those of your allies are made with a cumulative +2 bonus (in addition to the normal bonus provided by charging). An opponent struck by you and at least one other ally is stunned for 1 round. You and your allies do not provoke attacks of opportunity for moving as part of this charge.																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.94				ASPECT:Initiation Action|1 full-round action	ASPECT:Range|Melee attack; see text	ASPECT:Target Area|One creature; see text																							SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Warblade=9|WAR MASTER'S CHARGE
White Raven Hammer					KEY:Warblade Martial Discipline ~ White Raven Hammer					SORTKEY:Maneuvers and Stances	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Warblade Martial Maneuver.White Raven.White Raven Discipline.White Raven Maneuver.Maneuver.Martial Maneuver.Strike					PREABILITY:3,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.White Raven Maneuver					PREVARGTEQ:InitiatorManueverLVL,8		DESC:You slam your opponent with a mighty attack to disrupt his senses and leave him unable to defend himself while your allies close to finish him off. As part of this maneuver, you make a single, devastating strike against an opponent. The raw force of this blow knocks him senseless. Your attack deals an extra 6d6 points of damage and stuns your opponent for 1 round.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.94				ASPECT:Initiation Action|1 standard action	ASPECT:Range|Melee attack	ASPECT:Target Area|One creature	ASPECT:Duration|1 round																					SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Warblade=8|WHITE RAVEN HAMMER
White Raven Strike					KEY:Warblade Martial Discipline ~ White Raven Strike					SORTKEY:Maneuvers and Stances	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Warblade Martial Maneuver.White Raven.White Raven Discipline.White Raven Maneuver.Maneuver.Martial Maneuver.Strike					PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.White Raven Maneuver					PREVARGTEQ:InitiatorManueverLVL,4		DESC:Your eye for tactics allows you to notice an enemy's weak points and attack them with a mighty blow. The White Raven discipline focuses on tactics, teamwork, and the ability to make an attack that improves your allies' abilities. This strike ruins a foe's defenses. As part of this maneuver, you make a single melee attack. If it hits, you deal an extra 4d6 points of damage, and the target is considered flat-footed until the start of his next turn.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.94				ASPECT:Initiation Action|1 standard action	ASPECT:Range|Melee attack	ASPECT:Target Area|One creature																									SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Warblade=4|WHITE RAVEN STRIKE
White Raven Tactics					KEY:Warblade Martial Discipline ~ White Raven Tactics					SORTKEY:Maneuvers and Stances	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Warblade Martial Maneuver.White Raven.White Raven Discipline.White Raven Maneuver.Maneuver.Martial Maneuver.Boost					PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.White Raven Maneuver					PREVARGTEQ:InitiatorManueverLVL,3		DESC:You can inspire your allies to astounding feats of martial prowess. With a few short orders, you cajole them into seizing the initiative and driving back the enemy. Your knowledge of tactics can aid your allies' attacks, and it also allows you to spot, predict, and counter your enemies' actions. In the chaos of battle, you impose the order needed for tight, effective group tactics. When you use this maneuver, select an ally within range. Her initiative count immediately equals your initiative count -1. She then acts on her new initiative count as normal. If she has already acted in the current round, she can act again. If this maneuver would not change your ally's initiative count, it has no effect. If she has not yet acted during this round, her initiative count changes, and she acts on that count as normal. She does not act again on her original initiative count.																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.94				ASPECT:Initiation Action|1 swift action	ASPECT:Range|10 ft.	ASPECT:Target Area|One ally																												SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Warblade=3|WHITE RAVEN TACTICS
