Radiant Charge						KEY:Jade Phoenix Mage Martial Discipline ~ Radiant Charge					SORTKEY:Maneuvers and Stances	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Devoted Spirit.Devoted Spirit Discipline.Jade Phoenix Mage Martial Maneuver.Devoted Spirit Maneuver.Maneuver.Martial Maneuver.Strike				PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.Devoted Spirit Maneuver	PREALIGN:LG,NG,CG	PREVARGTEQ:InitiatorManueverLVL,5		DESC:You gather the power of your faith and discipline, surrounding yourself in an aura of blinding glory. You must make a charge attack as part of this maneuver. If the target is evilaligned, your attack deals an extra 6d6 points of damage. In addition, if your charge attack hits and the target is evil-aligned, you become wreathed in holy energy. You gain damage reduction 10/- until the beginning of your next turn.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.60				ASPECT:Descriptor|Good	ASPECT:Initiation Action|1 full-round action	ASPECT:Range|Melee attack	ASPECT:Target Area|One creature	ASPECT:Duration|1 round																	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Jade Phoenix Mage=5|RADIANT CHARGE
Rallying Strike						KEY:Jade Phoenix Mage Martial Discipline ~ Rallying Strike					SORTKEY:Maneuvers and Stances	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Devoted Spirit.Devoted Spirit Discipline.Jade Phoenix Mage Martial Maneuver.Devoted Spirit Maneuver.Maneuver.Martial Maneuver.Strike				PREABILITY:2,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.Devoted Spirit Maneuver				PREVARGTEQ:InitiatorManueverLVL,6		DESC:Your weapon blazes with divine energy as you smite your enemy. The energy discharges in a great pulse, sweeping over your allies and mending their wounds. As part of initiating this strike, you must make a successful melee attack against an enemy whose alignment has at least one component different from yours. This foe must pose a threat to you or your allies in some direct, immediate way. If your attack hits, you and all allies within 30 feet of you heal 3d6 points of damage + 1 point per initiator level (maximum +15).																																																																																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.60				ASPECT:Initiation Action|1 standard action	ASPECT:Range|Melee attack	ASPECT:Target Area|One creature																									SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Jade Phoenix Mage=6|RALLYING STRIKE
Revitalizing Strike					KEY:Jade Phoenix Mage Martial Discipline ~ Revitalizing Strike					SORTKEY:Maneuvers and Stances	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Devoted Spirit.Devoted Spirit Discipline.Jade Phoenix Mage Martial Maneuver.Devoted Spirit Maneuver.Maneuver.Martial Maneuver.Strike				PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.Devoted Spirit Maneuver				PREVARGTEQ:InitiatorManueverLVL,3		DESC:As you rear back to strike your foe, an aura of divine energy surrounds you. As your attack slams home, this aura dissipates in a flash, knitting your wounds as it discharges. As part of initiating this strike, you must make a successful melee attack against an enemy creature whose alignment has at least one component different from yours. This foe must pose a threat to you or your allies in some direct, immediate way. If your attack hits, you or an ally within 10 feet of you heals 3d6 points of damage + 1 point per initiator level (maximum +10).																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.60				ASPECT:Initiation Action|1 standard action	ASPECT:Range|Melee attack	ASPECT:Target Area|One creature																									SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Jade Phoenix Mage=3|REVITALIZING STRIKE
Shield Block						KEY:Jade Phoenix Mage Martial Discipline ~ Shield Block						SORTKEY:Maneuvers and Stances	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Devoted Spirit.Devoted Spirit Discipline.Jade Phoenix Mage Martial Maneuver.Devoted Spirit Maneuver.Maneuver.Martial Maneuver.Counter																			PREVARGTEQ:InitiatorManueverLVL,2		DESC:With a heroic burst of effort, you thrust your shield between your defenseless ally and your enemy. As an immediate action, you can grant an AC bonus to an adjacent ally equal to your shield's AC bonus + 4. You apply this bonus in response to a single melee or ranged attack that targets your ally. You can initiate this maneuver after an opponent makes his attack roll, but you must do so before you know whether the attack was a success or a failure.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.60				ASPECT:Initiation Action|1 immediate action	ASPECT:Range|Personal	ASPECT:Target Area|You	ASPECT:Duration|Instantaneous																							SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Jade Phoenix Mage=2|SHIELD BLOCK
Shield Counter						KEY:Jade Phoenix Mage Martial Discipline ~ Shield Counter					SORTKEY:Maneuvers and Stances	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Devoted Spirit.Devoted Spirit Discipline.Jade Phoenix Mage Martial Maneuver.Devoted Spirit Maneuver.Maneuver.Martial Maneuver.Counter				PREABILITY:2,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.Devoted Spirit Maneuver				PREVARGTEQ:InitiatorManueverLVL,7		DESC:As your opponent prepares to make his attack, you bash him with your shield and disrupt his attempt. As an immediate action, you can attempt a shield bash against an opponent you threaten. This attack is made with a -2 penalty. If your shield attack hits, your target's next attack automatically misses. You can use this maneuver immediately after an opponent declares an attack, but you must do so before the attack's result has been determined.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.60				ASPECT:Initiation Action|1 immediate action	ASPECT:Range|Melee attack	ASPECT:Target Area|One creature																									SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Jade Phoenix Mage=7|SHIELD COUNTER
